Very cool!  I'm planning on starting a falconry apprenticeship this year or next in hopes of trapping (25 permits issued province wide annually) a wild red tail to train for rabbit and crow hunting. Need to wait until we move though...can't keep hawks, eagles, or falcons in Brantford.
